Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway welcome back special guest Kansas City sports radio host GAT to discuss her beloved Chiefs and their shot at getting Jalen Ramsey, why we said last weekend was the ultimate betting trap, Ross' hatred for the Seattle Seahawks, and we drop all the spreads for this weekends College Football and NFL slate.
